TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Post SQL
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: BEGIN MERGE [Staging].[sls].[CreditCard] AS tgt USING [Staging].[sls].[CreditCard_diff] AS src ON ( tgt.[CreditCardID] = src.[CreditCardID] ) WHEN MATCHED AND EXISTS ( SELECT src.[CardType], src.[CardNumber], src.[ExpMonth], src.[ExpYear], src.[ModifiedDate] EXCEPT SELECT tgt.[CardType], tgt.[CardNumber], tgt.[ExpMonth], tgt.[ExpYear], tgt.[ModifiedDate] ) THEN UPDATE SET [CardType] = src.[CardType] ,[CardNumber] = src.[CardNumber] ,[ExpMonth] = src.[ExpMonth] ,[ExpYear] = src.[ExpYear] ,[ModifiedDate] = src.[ModifiedDate] ,[AUD_LastModDatetime] = src.[AUD_LastModDatetime] WHEN NOT MATCHED BY TARGET THEN INSERT ([CreditCardID] ,[CardType] ,[CardNumber] ,[ExpMonth] ,[ExpYear] ,[ModifiedDate] ,[AUD_CreateDatetime] ,[AUD_LastModDatetime] ) VALUES (src.[CreditCardID] ,src.[CardType] ,src.[CardNumber] ,src.[ExpMonth] ,src.[ExpYear] ,src.[ModifiedDate] ,src.[AUD_CreateDatetime] ,src.[AUD_LastModDatetime] ) WHEN NOT MATCHED BY SOURCE THEN UPDATE SET [AUD_isDeleted] = 1 ,[AUD_LastModDatetime] = GETDATE()\; END;

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Post SQL
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: BEGIN MERGE [Staging].[sls].[Customer] AS tgt USING [Staging].[sls].[Customer_diff] AS src ON ( tgt.[CustomerID] = src.[CustomerID] ) WHEN MATCHED AND EXISTS ( SELECT src.[PersonID], src.[StoreID], src.[TerritoryID], src.[AccountNumber], src.[rowguid], src.[ModifiedDate] EXCEPT SELECT tgt.[PersonID], tgt.[StoreID], tgt.[TerritoryID], tgt.[AccountNumber], tgt.[rowguid], tgt.[ModifiedDate] ) THEN UPDATE SET [PersonID] = src.[PersonID] ,[StoreID] = src.[StoreID] ,[TerritoryID] = src.[TerritoryID] ,[AccountNumber] = src.[AccountNumber] ,[rowguid] = src.[rowguid] ,[ModifiedDate] = src.[ModifiedDate] ,[AUD_LastModDatetime] = src.[AUD_LastModDatetime] WHEN NOT MATCHED BY TARGET THEN INSERT ([CustomerID] ,[PersonID] ,[StoreID] ,[TerritoryID] ,[AccountNumber] ,[rowguid] ,[ModifiedDate] ,[AUD_CreateDatetime] ,[AUD_LastModDatetime] ) VALUES (src.[CustomerID] ,src.[PersonID] ,src.[StoreID] ,src.[TerritoryID] ,src.[AccountNumber] ,src.[rowguid] ,src.[ModifiedDate] ,src.[AUD_CreateDatetime] ,src.[AUD_LastModDatetime] ) WHEN NOT MATCHED BY SOURCE THEN UPDATE SET [AUD_isDeleted] = 1 ,[AUD_LastModDatetime] = GETDATE()\; END;

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Post SQL
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: BEGIN MERGE [Staging].[sls].[SalesPersonQuotaHistory] AS tgt USING [Staging].[sls].[SalesPersonQuotaHistory_diff] AS src ON ( tgt.[BusinessEntityID] = src.[BusinessEntityID] AND tgt.[QuotaDate] = src.[QuotaDate] ) WHEN MATCHED AND EXISTS ( SELECT src.[SalesQuota], src.[rowguid], src.[ModifiedDate] EXCEPT SELECT tgt.[SalesQuota], tgt.[rowguid], tgt.[ModifiedDate] ) THEN UPDATE SET [SalesQuota] = src.[SalesQuota] ,[rowguid] = src.[rowguid] ,[ModifiedDate] = src.[ModifiedDate] ,[AUD_LastModDatetime] = src.[AUD_LastModDatetime] WHEN NOT MATCHED BY TARGET THEN INSERT ([BusinessEntityID] ,[QuotaDate] ,[SalesQuota] ,[rowguid] ,[ModifiedDate] ,[AUD_CreateDatetime] ,[AUD_LastModDatetime] ) VALUES (src.[BusinessEntityID] ,src.[QuotaDate] ,src.[SalesQuota] ,src.[rowguid] ,src.[ModifiedDate] ,src.[AUD_CreateDatetime] ,src.[AUD_LastModDatetime] ) WHEN NOT MATCHED BY SOURCE THEN UPDATE SET [AUD_isDeleted] = 1 ,[AUD_LastModDatetime] = GETDATE()\; END;
